chnology in China">History of science and technology in China</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Technology_of_the_Song_dynasty" class="mw-redirect" title="Technology of the Song dynasty">Technology of the Song dynasty</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dream_Pool_Essays&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span id="cnote_a"><b><a href="#ref_a">^</a></b></span>&#160;<b>a:</b>&#160;<i>Shen Gua (1031\xe2\x80\x931091) et les Sciences, Revue d\'Histoire des Sciences et de Leurs Applications</i> (1989)<br /></li>\n<li><span id="cnote_b"><b><a href="#ref_b">^</a></b></span>&#160;<b>b:</b>&#160;<i>Floril\xc3\xa8ge des notes du Ruisseau des r\xc3\xaaves (</i>Mengxi bitan<i>) de Shen Gua (1031\xe2\x80\x931095)</i> by Jean-Fran\xc3\xa7ois Billete and 31 of his <a href="/wiki/Geneva_University" class="mw-redirect" title="Geneva University">Geneva University</a> students, in <i>\xc3\x89tudes Asiatiques</i> (1993)<br /></li>\n<li><span id="cnote_i"><b><a href="#ref_i">^</a></b></span>&#160;<b>i:</b>&#160;See <a href="/wiki/Greek_fire" title="Greek fire">Greek fire</a><br /></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dream_Pool_Essays&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: References">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Citations">Citations</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dream_Pool_Essays&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Citations">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class="reflist columns references-column-widt